quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Min nulaali jeertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wonaa hooree…ďe ma…ď…ďe neemii…ďe mbi'ay: "Minen Min tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen e diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin men √Īermtinta"."
  43,24,"O maaki: "Hay si mi addan on ko …ďuri feewude kon ko tawru…óon baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen?" ∆Āe mbi'i: "Minen dey, ko min jeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon e mum koon"."
  43,25,"Min njottii e ma…ď…ďe. ndaare no battande fennu…ďe …ďeen mba'unoo."
  43,26,"JaŇčto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo been makko e yim…ďe makko …ďeen: "Min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e kon ko ndewoton,"
  43,27,"si wanaa On tak…óo lam, KaŇčko oon, O feewnay kam"."
  43,28,"O wa…ói ngool konngol heddotoongol …ďaawo makko, mbelajo'o, …ďe nduttoto."
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii …ďee …óoo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, haa nde goonga kan ngarnoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo."
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'i: "∆äuum ko mbilewu, minen ko min njeddu…ďe …óuum"."
  43,31,"∆Āe mb'iti: "Ko ha…óno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko maw…óo ca'e …óen …ói…ói?""
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen? Awa ko Minen ngoni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óiin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Min …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko ko …ďe moo…ďata."
  43,33,"Si wonaano fii wata yim…ďe …ďeen ngon mofte goote, Min mba…óayno e cuu…ói kala jeddu…óo Hinnaranke Oon: ki…ď…ďe kaalisi e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra;"